
  Package Contents
  ----------------

  This package contains a library of models for RooFit. For instructions
  on compiling and using this package, please read the README of RooFitCore.
  

  How to write your own PDF
  -------------------------

  Consult the 'RooFit programmers tutorial' available on the RooFit tutorials page: 
  http://roofit.sourceforge.net/docs/tutorial/prog


  Contributions
  -------------

  If you have developed a PDF class that you think might be of interest to other users,
  and is well debugged and documented, you can have your class included in the 
  RooFitModels package. Please contact us for details.